---
title: Roast Pumpkin & Courgette Ribbon Salad with Feta, Mint & Flaked Almonds
description: This vibrant roast pumpkin and courgette ribbon salad is a celebration of fresh, earthy flavours, complemented by creamy feta and fragrant mint. Topped with crunchy almonds, it’s a delightful mix of textures and tastes that’s as refreshing as it is satisfying.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*
